certificate page

  As a user who completed the quiz for a course, and,
  as a user who purchased a certificate,
  I can see the certificate page for a course

Scenario:
  I can see a certificate
  I can see the name of the course
  I can see my name on the certificate
  I can see the date that I completed the course
  I can see the # of hours spent on the course
  I can see the CEU certification on the certificate
  i can see Bob Nelson's signature on certificate
  I can see a link to print the certificate
  I can see a link to email the certificate
  I can see a link to return to the course